499
00:35:40,140 --> 00:35:41,330
Kto ti to urobil?

500
00:35:42,130 --> 00:35:43,600
Mamička, nesmieš zomrieť.

501
00:35:49,470 --> 00:35:50,200
Mamička.

502
00:35:50,430 --> 00:35:51,590
Mami, si hore?

503
00:35:52,810 --> 00:35:54,510
Vedel som, že by si neumrela.

504
00:35:54,970 --> 00:35:56,510
Samozrejme, že nie, 
