00:41:35,200 --> 00:41:37,340
Vy ste ju prinútil.

533
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:39,990
A ona svedčila.

534
00:41:42,580 --> 00:41:45,060
Mal ste dodržať svoj sľub.

535
00:41:46,550 --> 00:41:47,890
"Dôverujte mi."

536
00:41:47,890 --> 00:41:49,670
